---
title: Prawn Red Thai Curry with Courgette, Carrot and Rice
description: You won’t believe this curry took 15 minutes to cook when you taste its incredible depth of flavour. Rich, warming and packed with fresh, flavourful ingredients, we predict that this recipe will become your weeknight go-to in no time! With homemade food this fast, you can say goodbye to those takeaway daydreams.
